{ //Krobus

  //Krobus Gift Tastes
  "CDE_Krobus_GoldPumpkin": "The Wizard's maze held this prize at the end, didn't it? I suppose you could only find it if you're unafraid of the dark.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_RockCandy": "I've heard of these, but I've never tried one. *crunch*#$b#Ohhhh, hohoho, the power! Tonight is going to be a very interesting night!$6",
  "CDE_Krobus_PrismaticShard": "I can feel a beautiful, sacred energy emanating from this stone. What a rare and special item.",
  "CDE_Krobus_RabbitsFoot": "Humans keep these for luck, don't they? What an amusing practice!$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_VoidEgg": "What a kind gesture. I have these right here in my shop, but the giving of a void egg is a deep sign of respect for my people.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Diamond": "Diamonds are the earth itself, perfected and beautiful. It's very thoughtful of you to share.",
  "CDE_Krobus_IridiumBar": "Deep from the earth's darkest depths, these iridium bars make marvelous gifts.#$e#Normally, they're reserved for royalty, but I don't mind.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Pumpkin": "This reminds me of that festival you do each year... Spirit's Eve, is it?#$b#I love watching that festival from the shadows. It's so cute how all the humans behave.$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_WildHorseradish": "Ah, this plant! The spicy flavor is so soothing... I won't have to worry about my mischievous side getting away from me.",

  //Krobus's Misc Dialogue
  //these lines target files other than the standard characters/dialogue/Krobus location such as unmarried rainy dialogue
  "CDE_Krobus_rainy_1": "Ah, the sewers are flowing quickly today. It'll get nice and humid in here... Just how I like it.",
  "CDE_Krobus_rainy_2": "Rain is truly a lifegiving force. Give thanks to Yoba today.",
  "CDE_Krobus_rainy_3": "Today might be a good day for me to poke me head outside for a few minutes.#$e#...If the coast is clear, that is.",

