  //Special Dialogue
  "CDE_Krobus_repeated_1":"If you put your ear up to the right pipe, you can hear into any house from down here.#$b#I wouldn't eavesdrop, though!$3",
  "CDE_Krobus_repeated_2":"Please don't tell anyone about me.#$b#Most humans are frightened by us shadow people... maybe for good reason.$s#$b#But regardless, if the townspeople knew about me, I might not be safe here.",
