  //heart specific dialogue
  "CDE_Krobus_Mon10":"'Krobus' means 'bridge-crosser' in our language.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Mon8":"Dwarves? The dwarves slew us indiscriminately for ages, violent and non-violent alike.$a#$e#Please, I wish to have no more talk on this painful topic.$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_Mon6":"My friends and I have largely been shunned by our kind, for attempting to suppress our chaotic nature.#$e#But I cannot declare myself better than the violent ones. A life is a life.#$e#Please, even if you have slain any violent ones, I do not wish to know.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Mon4":"...Have you encountered others like me, in the mines? I'm sorry if they were hostile towards you. You see, we've learned to fear humans... there have been too many... unpleasant encounters.$s#$e#You haven't... slain any of my friends, have you?$3",
  "CDE_Krobus_Tue10":"@, I have grown quite amiable of your frequent visits here.#$e#It is strange. Until recently, I never would have even considered friendship with a human.",  
  "CDE_Krobus_Tue8":"Rasmodius is a good man. He is one of the few humans besides you whom I would trust.#$e#His worldview is in much better alignment with reality than most humans'.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Tue6":"Yes, I call this place my home.#$e#I did not have a place to call my home for quite some time.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Tue4":"There is a plant that grows in the springtime. Humans describe it as \"spicy,\" but for my kind, we find it...#$b#How shall I put it? It keeps the evil instincts at bay.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Tue2":"So you farm for a living? I occasionally carry a product that might help you. Check back on Friday.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Wed10":"You've seen Junimo, too? I'm surprised. For a human, you seem to have quite a propensity for encountering elementals.",  
  "CDE_Krobus_Wed8":"A while ago, two human children contemplated finding a way in here.#$e#Regretfully, I had to scare them away. There would be no chance of them keeping my secrecy.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Wed6":"In rare cases, some tricksters belonging to my kind have made sport out of hiding in children's closets and scaring them at night.#$b#I do not condone any such kind of behavior.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Wed4":"A 1000 year war between my people and the dwarves recently ended. There's still a lot of resentment on both sides.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Wed2":"Sometimes, objects come floating down the water and I collect them.#$b#I can also move freely within the shadows, unencumbered by gravity, which lets me sustain trade with others and rotate my stock.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Thu2":"I hope you appreciate the risk I took with you, by not fleeing when you first appeared down here.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Thu8":"I have observed your kind for many years. It has given me ample opportunity to learn your language.#$e#However, you are one of the first humans with whom I have had consistent interaction.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Thu6":"I don't think you will find many interesting fish in this kind of water.#$e#I did see a rather large, strange looking fish swimming around, but just once.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Thu4":"No, we are not born from a mother like you humans are.#$e#Where do we come from, then? Well, when does any shadow begin to exist?#$b#Are the shadows under your feet somehow \"new,\" or simply less hidden by the light?#$e#Likewise, when does any soul begin to exist?#$e#That said, I somewhat arbitrarily credit the start of winter as the time when my essence hatched from the darkness.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Sat10":"Thank you for being respectful toward my devotion of silence on Fridays.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Sat8":"I thank Yoba for bringing clarity to my chaotic nature.#$b#Without a doubt, I would have earned the title \"shadow brute\" long ago if not for her blessings and guidance.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Sat6":"Humans have some rather interesting customs for showing respect to Yoba.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Sun6":"I have safeguarded the Return Scepter for many years. Its origin predates both our species, significantly.#$e#As such, I hope you understand why I cannot sell it for an ordinary price.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Sun2":"Please keep my location a secret. If the dwarves knew of me, they'd surely send an assassin.",
  "CDE_Krobus_summerMon10":"Do you, too, feel comfortable in the darkness? I heard the human body needs sunlight to stay healthy. Is it harmful for you to spend too much time down here?",
  "CDE_Krobus_summerTue10":"I know that I cannot spend too much time in the sun. Can you not spend much time in the dark?",
  "CDE_Krobus_summerSat8": "I'll never know what it's like to be human... but talking to you, I feel like I understand it a little.",
  "CDE_Krobus_summerSun10":"It's in my nature to create chaos. And sometimes I still feel an urge for mischief.$6#$b#...$3#$b#But you're here now. And when you visit me, the urge suddenly dissipates.#$e#Is there something wrong with me?$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_fallMon10":"Seems you may have found some secret notes.#$e#Yes, I apologize. Some of my kind enjoy snatching notes from humans' houses at night. We sometimes discard them in unusual places.",
  "CDE_Krobus_fallWed10":"Heeheehee. Dogs... AND cats... have pointy ears...$7#$b#...on top of their heads!$7#$e#It's so cute! I can hardly stand it.$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_fallThu10":"There are plenty of delicious things to eat down here. Flies. Slugs. Roaches.#$e#Recently, I saw a mantis who was lost.",
  "CDE_Krobus_fallSat10":"I decided upon the name \"Krobus\" for myself. This was only a few hundred years ago.#$e#Before then, I had other names. ...I think.#$b#Or maybe I didn't have a name before \"Krobus.\" It's tough to remember.$3",
  "CDE_Krobus_fallSun10":"We shadow beings don't grow old. We can \"pass away,\" though not in the same way as your kind.#$e#With time, we slowly dissolve until we are indistinguishable from the darkness once again.#$b#Some time later, a new shadow being hatches from the darkness.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_winterMon10":"Many shadow beings enjoy \"Strange Bun.\" I certainly do, too.#$b#But humans probably don't like them. Too bad, they're delicious.$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_winterTue10":"It's too cold for the tiny bugs to survive. My food supply is a bit short.$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_winterSat10":"I carry mixed feelings about my species. On one hand, I'm ashamed of the chaos we've caused. It's simply in our nature.$3#$b#But we're not all violent. And my kin, my origin... it's who I am. I can't just forsake where I come from, can I?$3",

