  //Krobus's Married Dialogue

  //weather specific dialogue
  
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_1": "The raindrops tickle when I step outside. I might go for a walk.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_2": "Do you like rainy days as much as I do, @?",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_3": "We're different in so many ways... but that's alright.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_4": "When I look up at the dark clouds, I wonder if there are cloud beings who live up there.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_5": "I'm happy here, in the house. I like to spend all my time in a good spot... I don't need to \"get out\" like humans do.#$e#But I understand that you need to! Please don't feel like you have to stay here with me.$3",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_6": "I wonder if the wizard knows about... this? I hope he can keep a secret.$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_7": "I love the rain, but it sure looks lonely outside. Nice to have someone like you for company.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_8": "As much as I try to be civilized, I have the urge to be mischievous sometimes...$6#$e#They say it's a condition of my people.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_9": "Ah, it's more humid today with the rain... I feel a lot more comfortable.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyDay_10": "Anything I can help with while you're out today?",

  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_1": "On nights like this, those who gaze out windows sometimes see shadowy figures. To think... it might've been me.$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_2": "It's a bit spooky out there, isn't it? I can understand it from a human's perspective these days, at least a little.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_3": "If the other shadow people knew of our living arrangement, they would... \"punish\" me. Most of them despise humans, you know.$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_4": "I hope you stayed safe today. I assume you did?",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_5": "You're sopping wet, and cold! Isn't that dangerous to your species?$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_6": "In a hundred years, who knows? Maybe our living arrangement will be quite normal.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_7": "I already had dinner, but it wasn't something you'd be able to eat... sorry.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_8": "I tried to watch a \"movie\" on the... \"television.\" It wasn't my favorite, but I'm glad I tried.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_9": "Sometimes I wonder if humans and shadow people could really ever co-exist... It's a lovely idea, but is it realistic?$s#$e#I hope so...",",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_10": "It's said that my people came here long ago, when a great catastrophe allowed spirits from the void to cross into the physical plane.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_11": "What's the word for it again? ... \"Cozy.\" Right. That's how it is in here tonight.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_RainyNight_12": "The sound of the rain reminds me of the sewers... it's comforting.#$e#The sewers were my refuge... I felt safe there. But don't worry... I feel the same way about my new home, too.",

  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_1": "If I could come help you, I would... but I'll do my best to keep the house in order.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_2": "Am I leaving too much void dust around the house? I'll clean it up if you need me to.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_3": "I tried my best to make human food... [203 204 651 225] You can eat it later, don't worry about it...",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_4": "Well, I made this. [204 651 225]It tastes good to me, but... no pressure.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_5": "I went exploring last night and found this. [305 308 203 795 397]Think you could use it?",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_6": "Good morning, @. I went out before the sun and found this for you. [305 308 203 795 397]I hope it's not too strange.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_7": "Don't worry, I won't be bored today. A human's desire for novelty is much higher than mine.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_8": "I don't like coffee much, but I thought you might like some. So... here you go. [395]",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_9": "On Fridays, I like to stay quiet out of respect for Yoba. I hope you don't mind.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_10": "Ooh, there's so much sun! ...But I can tolerate it a bit better than I used to.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_11": "I wish I could help you on the farm, but I can't go out in the sun...",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorDay_12": "Good morning. Say hi to all the animals for me.",

  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_1": "I cleaned all the bugs out of the house today... Sorry, I didn't save you any! *smack*$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_2": "Ooh, it's nice to have you back home again. Are you staying in?$l",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_3": "You feel solid... sometimes I wish I had bones, too...$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_4": "I'm sure it's my mind playing a trick, but lately I do feel a bit more... corporeal than usual.$l",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_5": "Ever since I left my people, I've been searching for a new home... now I belong somewhere. That means everything to me.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_6": "What a beautiful night.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_7": "I have vague memories from ancient times, but they're all so faded. I don't think I could articulate them.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_8": "I looked out the window today and I saw %pet running around. So cute!$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_9": "I remember when I first learned the sound of your footsteps approaching me in the sewer. Such a fond memory.$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_10": "This week, I pray that the will of Yoba shall be done. Whatever her will may be, I shall be ready.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_IndoorNight_11": "Hi, @. Welcome home. You look like you've been working hard out there!$h",
  
