  //Date Specific Dialogue
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_spring1":"What's your plan for the new year, @?",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_spring6":"Humans and shadow beings have such different traditions in worshipping Yoba. And yet, Yoba created both our species.#$e#Perhaps Yoba is much more complex than most of us realize.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_spring15":"I just want to live my life doing right by Yoba. I never wanted to be an agent of chaos.$s#$e#But then I think... isn't it Yoba who made the shadow brutes? And made me the way I am? Sometimes it's all so confusing.$3#$e#Then again... Yoba brought you to me, and I like living here with you.#$b#And that isn't so complicated, is it?$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_spring23":"You should go to the flower dance tomorrow! Don't worry about me.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_summer1":"I get sunburnt very easily, so I need to be careful this time of year.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_summer8":"Mmm... what's that lovely smell? You must've been sweating all night...$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_summer10":"I'm considering spending my day all balled up and wedged in the corner...#$e#What? You mean you don't do that?$3",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_summer15":"It's summer... that means the house is full of flies.#$e#Don't worry, I'll take care of them. It's good protein!$h",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_fall8":"I don't feel like doing anything today.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_fall15":"Have you figured out what you're going to use for your grange display tomorrow?",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_fall17":"Heeheehee... It's a great day for causing a little chaos for the citizens of Pelican Town...$6",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_fall18":"...I'm terribly sorry. I wasn't myself yesterday. Seems my chaotic instincts flared up a bit.$3#$e#I let the feeling pass through me. Honest! You can ask the townsfolk. No one saw me.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_fall24": "If I showed up to the Spirit's Eve festival they'd put me in a cage...$s",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_winter7":"I want to be a good housemate for you, but I never know if I'm doing well... *groan* $s#$e#I have a hard time understanding human expression. B... but... you're happy living with me?#$e#Okay!$7",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_winter16":"Sometimes I pause and think of all that I've learned about humans from you...#$b#I wish all my fellow shadow people could know this feeling.",
  "CDE_Krobus_Married_winter28": "Thanks for letting me stay here, @. I'm looking forward to another great year!$h",

